  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="page" n="4">
        <pb n="4"/>
        <ab xml:id="block_A" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F087c74bb-f911-4d63-90af-6e320d2b1653.jp2/2741,1917,1393,674/max/0/default.jpg">
          בָּרְכוּ אֶת יְיָ הַמְבֹרָךְ!<lb/>
        בָּרוּךְ יְיָ הַמְבֹרָךְ<lb/>
        לְעוֹלָם וָעֶד!
        </ab>
        <ab xml:id="block_B" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F087c74bb-f911-4d63-90af-6e320d2b1653.jp2/386,1981,1421,548/max/0/default.jpg">
          BAR’CHU et Adonai hamvorach!<lb/>
        Baruch Adonai ham&apos;vorach<lb/>
        l&apos;olam va-ed!
        </ab>
        <ab xml:id="block_C" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F087c74bb-f911-4d63-90af-6e320d2b1653.jp2/1094,2642,2265,620/max/0/default.jpg">
          PRAISE ADONAI to whom praise is due forever!<lb/>
        Praised be Adonai to whom praise is due,<lb/>
        now and forever!
        </ab>
        <ab xml:id="block_D" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F087c74bb-f911-4d63-90af-6e320d2b1653.jp2/676,968,3124,800/max/0/default.jpg">
          שְׁמַע וּבִרְכוֹתֶיהָ<lb/>
        T<lb/>
        SH&apos;MA UVIRCHOTEHA - SH&apos;MA AND ITS BLESSINGS
        </ab>
        <ab xml:id="block_E" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F087c74bb-f911-4d63-90af-6e320d2b1653.jp2/357,5524,3721,794/max/0/default.jpg">
          All holy acts require summoning.<lb/>
        For those who choose: The prayer leader at the word<lb/>
        Bar&apos;chu (the call to worship) bends<lb/>
        the knees and bows from the waist, and at &quot;Adonai stands straight. Baruch Adonai is the<lb/>
        communal response, whereupon the community repeats the choreography of the first line.
        </ab>
